"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1191/medium_square_medium_square_shiitake-mushrooms-test.jpg"},{"name":"Mushrooms Oyster Local","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1192/medium_square_medium_square_oyster-mushrooms.jpg"},{"name":"Mushrooms Cremini Local","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1190/medium_square_medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"smoked paprika","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/10/medium_square_SMOKED_PAPRIKA_copy.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":[],"pantry_items_full":[],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/10198/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients_1.jpg","description":"Preheat oven to 425°F. Peel \u003cb\u003eshallot\u003c/b\u003e, halve, and thinly slice. Wipe \u003cb\u003emushrooms\u003c/b\u003e clean with a damp paper towel and roughly chop, discarding tough stems (see Recipe Tip). Halve \u003cb\u003elemon\u003c/b\u003e. Strip \u003cb\u003ethyme\u003c/b\u003e leaves, discarding stems. Rinse \u003cb\u003echives\u003c/b\u003e and thinly slice. Rinse \u003cb\u003elettuce\u003c/b\u003e, pat dry with paper towel, and cut into .5-inch slices. "},{"title":"Roast Mushrooms","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/10201/recipe_card_size_2._Roast_Mushrooms_1.jpg","description":"On a baking sheet, toss \u003cb\u003emushrooms\u003c/b\u003e with \u003cb\u003espice mix\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003ethyme\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003e1.5 tablespoons olive oil\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003e.5 teaspoon kosher salt\u003c/b\u003e, and \u003cb\u003epepper\u003c/b\u003e as desired. Arrange in a single layer and transfer to oven. Roast until tender, about 12 minutes, then remove. Transfer mushrooms to a plate and set aside, then increase oven temperature to 450°F."},{"title":"Make Dressing","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/10202/recipe_card_size_3._Make_Dressing_1.jpg","description":"While mushrooms roast, heat \u003cb\u003e2 teaspoons olive oil\u003c/b\u003e in a small pan over medium-high heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cb\u003eshallot\u003c/b\u003e. Sauté, stirring, until softening, 3-5 minutes. Add \u003cb\u003e.5 of agave\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003ejuice of 1 lemon\u003c/b\u003e. Cook until reduced by .5, about 1 minute. Transfer to a large bowl. Add \u003cb\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/b\u003e and whisk to combine. Season with \u003cb\u003e.125 teaspoon kosher salt\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003epepper\u003c/b\u003e as desired. Use remaining agave to sweeten a cup of tea."},{"title":"Assemble Toasts","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/10203/recipe_card_size_4._Assemble_Toasts_1.jpg","description":"Spread \u003cb\u003emustard\u003c/b\u003e over 1 side of each bread slice. Sprinkle over \u003cb\u003eGruyère\u003c/b\u003e, then add \u003cb\u003eroasted mushrooms\u003c/b\u003e, dividing evenly."},{"title":"Bake Toasts","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/10204/recipe_card_size_5._Broil_Toasts_1.jpg","description":"Wipe baking sheet from mushrooms clean and add \u003cb\u003etoasts\u003c/b\u003e mushroom-side up. Transfer to oven and bake until cheese is bubbling and mushrooms are crisp, about 7 minutes. "},{"title":"Plate Toasts","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/10196/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Toasts_1.jpg","description":"Add \u003cb\u003elettuce\u003c/b\u003e to bowl with dressing and toss to coat. Garnish \u003cb\u003etoasts\u003c/b\u003e with \u003cb\u003echives\u003c/b\u003e. Serve with \u003cb\u003elittle gem salad\u003c/b\u003e alongside and enjoy some toasty bliss.\n"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"featured favorite","slug":"featured-favorite","hex_color":null}],"allergens":[],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Bread","slug":"bread","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"featured favorite","slug":"featured-favorite","hex_color":null}],"feature":[]}}